<L>__{exterior wolf's lair conference hut day}
<A>__{a light drizzle. a man jabbering in italian o.s. we get our first good look at the demolished briefing hut. that anyone survived is a miracle. officers crowd around the smoldering ruins, the fuhrer himself heading this procession. he wears new clothes, nodding, smiling politely to the jabbering italian o.s. a slight wince is the only indication that he was damn near blown to bits just hours ago. come around to reveal none other than benito mussolini speaking an incessant stream of italian. hitler's p.o.v. blissful silence. mussolini's blathering falls literally on deaf ears.}
